Spoon whipped topping evenly into 6 dessert dishes. Using back of spoon, spread whipped topping onto bottom and up side of each dish. Pour milk into medium bowl. Add dry pudding mix. Beat with wire whisk 2 minutes or until well blended. Let stand 5 minutes. Spoon pudding into center of whipped topping in each dish. Serve immediately or refrigerate until ready to serve. Store leftover desserts in refrigerator.